## 🔧 Required Libraries

To run this project, you need to install the following libraries in the Arduino IDE:

### 📦 Libraries

- **[Adafruit NeoPixel](https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_NeoPixel)**  
  _Used for controlling the RGB LED strip._

- **[DS1302 RTC Library](https://github.com/msparks/arduino-ds1302)**  
  _Used for reading real-time clock data from the DS1302 chip._

### 🧰 How to Install

1. 🟢 Open the **Arduino IDE**
2. 🛠 Go to **Tools → Manage Libraries**
3. 🔍 Search for `NeoPixel`
4. ✅ Click **Install**
5. Repeat the same steps for `DS1302`
